    <briefdescription>
<para>Interface for a trigger event class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The trigger event is a way of running a function call back on the main event thread of <ref refid="namespaceDali" kindref="compound">Dali</ref>. To create a trigger event use the factory interface. </para>
